Clean

wheeler_clean <- wheeler |> mutate(
  date_arrest = dmy_hms(date_arrest)
) |> select(
  -inc_index,
  -incident_no,
  -other_no,
  -event_no,
  -time_arrest,
  -offense,
  -date_1,
  -suffix,
  -geox,
  -geoy,
)
wheeler_clean

Export

wheeler_clean |> write_rds("data-processed/01-WheelerCounty.rds")
